0017FE  3               LAB_SPEEK:
0017FE  3               LAB_SPOKE:
0017FE  3               LAB_SCRCLR:
0017FE  3               LAB_SCREEN:
0017FE  3               LAB_PATTERN:
0017FE  3               LAB_PLOT:
0017FE  3               LAB_LOCATE:
0017FE  3               LAB_COLOR:
