0018A3  3               BCD_TO_HEX:
0018A3  3  85 12                STA     nums_2          ; Store in TEMP2
0018A5  3  29 F0                AND     #$F0
0018A7  3  4A                   LSR     A               ; (shift 1 times to /2)
0018A8  3  85 11                STA     nums_1          ; Store the /2 into TEMP
0018AA  3  4A                   LSR     A               ;
0018AB  3  4A                   LSR     A               ; Shift two more times to /8
0018AC  3  18                   CLC
0018AD  3  65 11                ADC     nums_1          ; add /8 + /2 to get /10
0018AF  3  85 11                STA     nums_1          ; Store tens digit into TEMP
0018B1  3  A5 12                LDA     nums_2          ; Get Ones
0018B3  3  29 0F                AND     #$0F
0018B5  3  18                   CLC
0018B6  3  65 11                ADC     nums_1
0018B8  3  60                   RTS                     ; Return from subroutine
